	(text_box "About:\n- Input of the battery. XT60 power connector + 8-pin JST connector for cell wirse + 2-pin JST connector for battery NTC\n\nDesign info:\n-If battery has less then 7 cells, then place jumper between cell connections which are not being used, e.g. for 5-cell battery jumpers between cells 6 and 7 and betwenn 5 and 6 need to be populated"
